          <p>Beyond awards, we translate arbitration agreements, witness statements, expert reports, and hearing transcripts. For ongoing proceedings, we offer <a href="/services/legal-translation/">legal translation retainer</a> arrangements to ensure consistent terminology and priority handling throughout your case.</p>
        </div>
